  "detailed_description": "Hexwielder is a fun auto-attacking Roguelite that dares you to survive against waves of powerful enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose Your Wielder!</strong></h2>Choose from a variety of classes each with different strengths. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980320/extras/4df40b6d72b576e51b35c632674a4b0e.poster.avif?t=1727442259\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980320/extras/4df40b6d72b576e51b35c632674a4b0e.webm?t=1727442259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980320/extras/4df40b6d72b576e51b35c632674a4b0e.mp4?t=1727442259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wield Arcane Spells!</strong></h2>Hurl fireballs, call down lightning, summon a swarm of bees! Gain powerful hexes to destroy your foes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980320/extras/784d5f558a2634b2d5039f7dfa9cbc87.poster.avif?t=1727442259\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980320/extras/784d5f558a2634b2d5039f7dfa9cbc87.webm?t=1727442259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980320/extras/784d5f558a2634b2d5039f7dfa9cbc87.mp4?t=1727442259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Increase Your Power!</strong></h2>Gain and purchase power-ups to help you survive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980320/extras/aa6c45f0e63b7db0c56a4ef541